The use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the application of the proposed approach for novel scene view synthesis suggests a possible connection to robotics (cs.RO).
